      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Denis Mendoza</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/File:DenisPMendoza.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/93/DenisPMendoza.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:DenisPMendoza.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Denis P. Mendoza <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Denis P. Mendoza</b>,<br />\na Filipino <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pyroprocessing\">pyroprocessing</a> engineer \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \nand as computer chess aficionado and tester interested in chess programming and high performance compiling of engines from source \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, \nespecially <a href=\"/Toga\" title=\"Toga\">Toga</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \nDenis also served as <a href=\"/Category:Opening_Book_Author\" title=\"Category:Opening Book Author\">book author</a> of <a href=\"/Gunnar_Harms\" title=\"Gunnar Harms\">Gunnar Harms'</a> <a href=\"/Bobcat\" title=\"Bobcat\">Bobcat</a> engine.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Denis_Mendoza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Denis_Mendoza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14921\">Strelka 1.8 UCI released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 07, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Strelka\" title=\"Strelka\">Strelka</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=15051\">Glaurung Lodz 2007 (unofficial Windows distribution)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 12, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Glaurung\" title=\"Glaurung\">Glaurung</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16549\">SIMD-oriented Fast Mersenne Twister (SFMT)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  September 19, 2007 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16802\">Profiling error with MSVC 2005</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 30, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=2923\">Chris Wirth's endgame tablebases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Endgame Tablebases</a>, December 13, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Chessterfield\" title=\"Chessterfield\">Chessterfield</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18506\">Scorpio 64 bit questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Scorpio\" title=\"Scorpio\">Scorpio</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=7065#p32462\">Amundsen 0.65 (released on January 11th 2008)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 15, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Amundsen\" title=\"Amundsen\">Amundsen</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=20737\">Toga's node search in mp-mode</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 19, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Toga\" title=\"Toga\">Toga</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=4219\">Other endgame tablebase generators</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Endgame Tablebases</a>, January 28, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Denis_Mendoza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=6477\">Rodent 0.11 for AMD compatibility</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, February 20, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Rodent\" title=\"Rodent\">Rodent</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=42481&amp;start=9\">Re: Rodent 0.11</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 22, 2012</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Denis_Mendoza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72927&amp;start=3\">Re: New ChessGUI opening book - Top10SuperGM2020.cgb</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 31, 2020</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72927&amp;start=6\">Re: New ChessGUI opening book - Top10SuperGM2020.cgb</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 01, 2020</dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Denis_Mendoza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120921001429/http://computerchessengines.webs.com/\">Denis Mendoza's Computer Chess Projects</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Denis_Mendoza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=2923\">Chris Wirth's endgame tablebases</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Denis P. Mendoza</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Endgame Tablebases</a>, December 13, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Chessterfield\" title=\"Chessterfield\">Chessterfield</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120921072218/http://computerchessengines.webs.com/aboutme.htm\">About Me - Denis Mendoza's Computer Chess Projects</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120921024643/http://computerchessengines.webs.com/otherchessengines.htm\">Other Chess engines - Denis Mendoza's Computer Chess Projects</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20120921003044/http://computerchessengines.webs.com/togachessengine.htm\">Toga chess engine - Denis Mendoza's Computer Chess Projects</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301091854\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 83/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 174/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7891-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301091854 and revision id 25038\n -->\n"
